544
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,357
Like your own mother.

545
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,429
[Sighing]

546
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,556
- Goodbye, Father.
- Goodbye.

547
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:05,438
