558
00:37:55,680 --> 00:37:57,432
O'MALLEY: Here's something
to tide you over.

559
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:58,555
But, Father...

560
00:37:58,640 --> 00:38:01,632
It's all right. It's not charity. It's a loan.

561
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:05,955
Thanks. I can use it.

562
00:38:07,160 --> 00:38:08,752
I appreciate it.

563
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:12,230
I guess there's a lot of things
I should have said to you...

564
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:15,915
advice and one thing or another.
But you wouldn't have paid any attention.

565
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:18,468
After all, you are <i>1</i>8, aren't you?

566
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:22,629
CAROL: Don't worry. I'll be all right.
O'MALLEY: Of course you will, Carol.

567
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:25,228
- I'll get by.
- Don't say that.

568
00:38:26,200 --> 00:38:28,668
O'MALLEY: Let us hear from you.
CAROL: All right, Father.

569
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:29,909
CAROL: Bye.
O'MALLEY: Bye, Carol.

570
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:34,076
[Church bell chiming]

571
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:36,950
[Boys chattering]

572
00:38:44,240 --> 00:38:45,719
Hey, fellas.

573
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,995
What are we doing
hanging around here for?

574
