00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:24,960
TONY: Took us to a baseball game?
ALL: Yeah.

586
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:27,873
TONY: Bought us hot dogs, didn't he?
ALL: Yeah.

587
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:30,190
TONY: He's gonna take us to a picture show,
