00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:17,551
What do you say?
You gonna give me a break?

623
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:19,870
Father, that depends. What is it?

624
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:22,076
How many of you here know
<i>Three Blind Mice?</i>

